Capital Markets

Company Overview of Stone Arch Capital, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Stone Arch Capital, LLC is a private equity firm specializing in buyout, industry consolidations, growth capital, recapitalizations, add-on acquisitions or product extensions, and public or private transactions in middle market companies. It does not invest in real estate, technology, and commodity industries. The firm prefers to invest in lower middle market companies. The firm also invests in diversification, passive stakeholder exit, growth capital, ESOP plan dissolution, and succession planning. It seeks to invest in manufacturing and service industries. The firm primarily invests in companies based in the Midwest region of the United States with a focus on Illinois, Iowa, Indiana, Kansa...
Stone Arch Capital, LLC is a private equity firm specializing in buyout, industry consolidations, growth capital, recapitalizations, add-on acquisitions or product extensions, and public or private transactions in middle market companies. It does not invest in real estate, technology, and commodity industries. The firm prefers to invest in lower middle market companies. The firm also invests in diversification, passive stakeholder exit, growth capital, ESOP plan dissolution, and succession planning. It seeks to invest in manufacturing and service industries. The firm primarily invests in companies based in the Midwest region of the United States with a focus on Illinois, Iowa, Indiana, Kansas, Michigan, Minnesota, Missouri, Nebraska, North Dakota, Ohio, South Dakota, and Wisconsin. Under unique circumstances, it also considers investments outside the Midwest. The firm typically invests between $10 and $25 million in companies with annual revenues between $15 million to $150 million and EBITDA between $3.5 million and $15 million. It invests in companies with enterprise values between $15 million and $100 million, having sustainable operating margins of usually 10 percent or higher. The firm seeks to take control minority or majority stake in its portfolio companies. It does not make any hostile transactions. Stone Arch Capital, LLC was founded in 2003 and is based in Minneapolis, Minnesota.
Detailed Description


800 Nicollet MallSuite 1150Minneapolis, MN 55402United StatesFounded in 2003



Phone: 612-317-2980

